---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { site } from '../../lib/site';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy Policy" noindex>
  <section class="section section--tight legal">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="updated">Last updated: [TODO: date]</p>

      <h2>Who we are</h2>
      <p>This website is operated on behalf of {site.title}, {site.role}, {site.council}.</p>

      <h2>What information we collect</h2>
      <p>
        When you use the contact, casework enquiry, or newsletter sign-up forms on this site, we
        collect the information you provide — typically your name, email address, and the content
        of your message, and for casework enquiries, your postal address and the type of issue
        you're raising. Form submissions are processed via Formspree, a third-party form service —
        see their privacy policy at formspree.io for details of how they handle data in transit.
      </p>

      <h2>How we use it</h2>
      <p>
        We use the information you submit only to respond to your enquiry, follow up on casework
        on your behalf with {site.council} or other relevant bodies, and — if you sign up for the
        newsletter — to send occasional updates, which you can unsubscribe from at any time.
      </p>

      <h2>How long we keep it</h2>
      <p>
        Casework correspondence is retained for as long as necessary to resolve your enquiry and
        for a reasonable period afterwards for reference, in line with standard councillor
        casework retention practice. [TODO: confirm exact retention period.]
      </p>

      <h2>Your rights</h2>
      <p>
        Under UK data protection law, you have the right to ask what personal data we hold about
        you, to have inaccurate data corrected, and to ask for it to be deleted, subject to any
        legal obligation to retain it. To exercise these rights, contact us at
        <a href={`mailto:${site.email}`}>{site.email}</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>See our <a href="/legal/cookies/">Cookie Policy</a> for details of cookies used on this site.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about this policy can be sent to <a href={`mailto:${site.email}`}>{site.email}</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .legal h2 { margin-top: 2rem; }
  .updated { color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; }
</style>
